info.name: Tutorial Spark demos - without white background
info.description: This style modifies the demo look in HTML5, CSS3, Javascript, jQuery previews and other founded by Google (e.g jQueryUI / twitterBootstrap) in course.
info.additionalInfo:
Errors 404 ("Not Found") are not triggered by this style - this is the lack of files on the page server and only the administrator of the page can help. Possible site is abandoned, hence there may be errors about the lack of files (it is possible that it has been bothered by the bots - loopholes in the security of the site / server). uBlock Origin Filter supplement: 
tutorialspark.com###mainblock:style(top: 0 !important; bottom: 1px !important;)
AdGuard AdBlocker Filter supplement: 
tutorialspark.com#$##mainblock { top: 0 !important; bottom: 1px !important; }
